title: Report: Orlando City eye Paris Saint-Germain star Ibrahimovic
text:
Report: Orlando City eye Paris Saint-Germain star Ibrahimovic FOXSports 3 hrs ago Â© Getty Images PARIS, FRANCE - OCTOBER 4: Zlatan Ibrahimovic of PSG (left) celebrates his goal with Angel Di Maria of PSG during the French Ligue 1 match between Paris Saint-Germain FC (PSG) and Olympique de Marseille at Parc des Princes stadium on October 4, 2015 in Paris, France. (Photo by Jean Catuffe/Getty Images)
Major League Soccer's Orlando City are reportedly hoping to sign Paris Saint-Germain and Sweden striker Zlatan Ibrahimovic when his current contract expires next summer.
AdChoices Orlando City are currently playing their first season in MLS and a move for one of soccer's superstars would be another statement of intent after the club signed Brazilian attacking midfielder Kaka ahead of their debut season in MLS.
Italian website Tutto Mercato Web reports Orlando City want to bring Ibrahimovic to Florida, and the story follows last week's report that the club's majority owner, Flavio Augusto Da Silva, also wants to sign Real Madrid's Portuguese star Cristiano Ronaldo.
